<title>CSS Masking: clip path with margin-box</title><meta name="assert">
<link rel="help" href="https://drafts.fxtf.org/css-masking-1/#the-clip-path">
<link rel="match" href="reference/green-100x100.html">
<link href="reference/green-100x100.html">

<style><style><style>
  .clipped {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    background-color: green;
    clip-path: margin-box;
    /* This outline draws far outside the margin box and should be partially clipped. */
    outline: 201px solid green;
    margin: 25px;
    /* Disables margin collapsing. */
    float: left;
  }
</style></style></style>
<div class="clipped"></div>
